dct_title_s: Map showing lines of geological sections and the relation of Trenton rock to sea level
dct_description_sm: Relation of Trenton rock to sea level shown with shading and contour lines. Map showing paths of the geological cross sections depicted in the illustrations of tables I-XVI in the 18th Annual report (1893) / Indiana. Department of Geology and Natural Resources. Detached from: Indiana's structural features as revealed by the drill / E. P. Cubberley. In Indiana Department of Geology and Natural Resources eighteenth annual report ... 1893. Indianapolis: Wm. B. Burford, 1894. Page 221.
Imprint: Indpls : lithographed by William B. Burford, [1894]; Imprint: [Indianapolis] : [Indiana, Dept. of Geology and Natural Resources], [1894]
dct_publisher_sm: Indiana. Department of Geology and Natural Resources
